{"title":"韶山，我想再看看你","authors":["张鹤"],"dates":[{"year":1983,"month":12,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"韶山，我想再看看你（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张鹤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿过历史的风云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"韶山，我想再看看你。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看看明净的蓝天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎样衬托你的绿水青山；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看看那所老屋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在花木掩映中何等朴素自"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"韶山，我想看看你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老屋温暖的檐下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可有乳燕呢喃？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屋前清澈的塘边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可有伢儿戏水？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山坡上那座普通的土坟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可有新编的花环？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"韶山，我想看看你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"焕然一新的陈列室，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎样昭示领袖的斗争实践？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的风云、集体的智慧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又怎样培育常青的真理之"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦，韶山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，你不再有人为的仙云缭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不再有虚幻的玄光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切都那么真切、亲近，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁不感到阵阵新风扑面？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，韶山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我真想再看看你……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走在绿荫里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论，无论我们走到那里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里总有他垂下的绿荫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿荫如盖，绿荫似云。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一根遒劲的枝条"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都在挥洒图画，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万张婆娑的叶片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"交织着春的神韵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈日下耕耘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿荫给我们送来轻风、芳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"芬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们神清志爽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去开垦新的处女地；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿荫为我们拂去热汗、沙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向新的高度进军。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们仰望绿荫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎能不追忆起创业艰辛？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎能不回想起雾满茂林……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论，无论我们走到那里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里总有他垂下的浓密的绿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荫……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}